Dialogue: 10,0:01:04.35,0:01:08.02,Top,,0,0,0,,I'm living my youth to the fullest, aiming to become a world-famous film director one day!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:08.02,0:01:11.80,Top,,0,0,0,,Are you ready for this second adventure of Koganei Junpei?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:12.75,0:01:13.78,Top,,0,0,0,,Start!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:27.35,0:01:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Junpei-kun, let's swim!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:29.73,0:01:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine by me!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:50.43,0:01:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Junpei-kun...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:51.86,0:01:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Miwa-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:11.91,0:02:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:28.41,0:02:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we're safe now.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.27,0:02:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.53,0:02:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna have some fun together in the cabin?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.86,0:02:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're in the mood for another round?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.23,0:02:49.52,Thought,,0,0,0,,Just a dream?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.06,0:02:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That fucking shark! Why'd he come along just as things were getting good?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.57,0:02:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Moron. Moron. {/caw, caw}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.17,0:03:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.55,0:03:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ribbit, ribbit.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.44,0:03:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, crap.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.99,0:03:09.15,Top,,0,0,0,,Chief! It's finished!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.15,0:03:11.00,Top,,0,0,0,,Shut up! It's still morning!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.41,0:03:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a little strung out.\N Don't mind me. {can't find where in manga this episode comes from, unsure}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.80,0:03:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.42,0:03:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The script for our next film!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.01,0:03:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A script, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.73,0:03:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.56,0:03:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Koganei, we're putting it on hold.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.68,0:03:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! On hold?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.19,0:03:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I chased after rabbits on that mountain {https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Furusato_(children's_song) - I have no idea why this is here or what's the joke}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.17,0:03:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But why are we putting it on{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.59,0:03:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got no money for it!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.01,0:03:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.44,0:03:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But didn't we make a ton on the last one?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.49,0:03:44.74,Top,,0,0,0,,All the profits went to paying off our debt.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.74,0:03:47.45,Top,,0,0,0,,So what are we gonna do now?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.45,0:03:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm thinking about,\N as the president!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.50,0:03:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh man, so that all-nighter was for nothing?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.71,0:04:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Junpei, it looks like you'd better start thinking about your future. {softly suggesting for him to look for a more promising occupation}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.50,0:04:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! To hear that from you...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.68,0:04:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning! Hi, everyone!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.85,0:04:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief? Chief, please use this.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.67,0:04:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not much, but it's all I have.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.54,0:04:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Awesome. Lucky!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.56,0:04:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish it were that simple, \Nbut I can't accept it.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.24,0:04:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.11,0:04:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Miwa, I appreciate the gesture, \Nbut no thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.48,0:04:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.34,0:04:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.86,0:04:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Productions won't go under so easily.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.12,0:04:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But do you have funds for the next project?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.34,0:04:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We do!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.71,0:04:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lying!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.96,0:04:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, gather round! {probs referencing something}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.93,0:04:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Friends. As you're well aware,\N Apollo Productions is facing a serious crisis.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.92,0:04:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to need your full support \Nif we're to get through this.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.39,0:04:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Our support? What sort of support?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.67,0:05:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,To put it simply, we'll all work part time to raise the funds.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.26,0:05:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Part time?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.45,0:05:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.57,0:05:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a cute one.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.43,0:05:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, stop! Please stop! Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.82,0:05:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.05,0:05:38.58,Top,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Miss.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.58,0:05:40.64,Top,,0,0,0,,Take care of the car.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.02,0:05:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.01,0:05:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.09,0:05:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! Go!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.28,0:05:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Miss. Let me help you.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.17,0:06:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! Go!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.01,0:06:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So sexy.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.29,0:06:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! Go!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.59,0:06:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry it's not much...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.98,0:06:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.12,0:06:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! I'm getting too excited!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.75,0:06:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.85,0:06:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are a funny boy.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.67,0:06:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Koganei Junpei.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.09,0:06:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss, you're the actress\N Mina Yoshiko, aren't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.81,0:06:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.92,0:06:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen all of your movies!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.46,0:07:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea I had fans among college students. I'm flattered.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.26,0:07:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not in college.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.70,0:07:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm training to be a film director.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.16,0:07:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a director wannabe?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.35,0:07:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I like you.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.76,0:07:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to dance?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.45,0:07:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Working at a host club to raise money.\NWhat a fall from grace!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.10,0:07:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not complaining.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.48,0:07:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you got to meet Mina Yoshiko?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.86,0:07:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Bingo! Correct!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.98,0:07:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.04,0:07:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I got her kerchief and business card. {had to drop "autographed" for CPS}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.29,0:07:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And she promised to introduce me \Nto her film industry friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.30,0:07:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just courtesy, you dumbass. {something said for politeness' sake; diplomatic language; honeyed words; lip service; empty compliment}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.94,0:07:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on, Chief!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.36,0:07:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's for work, but that's no excuse to drink yourself stupid.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.38,0:07:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Piss off! You think I can do\N this sort of thing sober?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.91,0:07:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let Apollo go down, \Neven if I have to drink myself into oblivion.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.54,0:07:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's for our precious company,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.72,0:08:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,that everyone worked so hard for...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.71,0:08:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.19,0:08:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, capital! Miwa-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.21,0:08:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Junpei-kun, how was your first day on the job?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.72,0:08:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you like this midnight dinner.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.49,0:08:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starting to plan our next film, \Nusing your scenario as a base.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.63,0:08:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My scenario, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.81,0:08:52.24,Thought,,0,0,0,,Being a director is about writing scenarios.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.24,0:08:54.97,Thought,,0,0,0,,I'll introduce you to my friends \Nin the film industry.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.43,0:08:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.03,0:09:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Where was it?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.40,0:09:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Not here.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.17,0:09:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! I'll fix this up and\N send it to Mina Yoshiko.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.44,0:09:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Time to double down on this!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.39,0:09:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Flying out into the world, Koganei Junpei!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.16,0:09:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll talk business with Coppola.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.45,0:09:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll shake hands with Spielberg!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.13,0:09:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And drink sake with Lucas!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.92,0:09:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I wish.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.13,0:09:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Three million! No, two would be enough. If only...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.45,0:09:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.75,0:09:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. No good? Thought so.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.07,0:10:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How should I introduce you?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.83,0:10:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Koganei Junpei. I called yesterday.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.78,0:10:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait just a moment.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.93,0:10:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, Madam is at her villa in Izu. {/sensei}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.67,0:10:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see. Then, will you give this to her when she's back?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.50,0:10:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Most certainly.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.90,0:10:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.31,0:10:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.43,0:10:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.37,0:10:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, go!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.35,0:10:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, go!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.77,0:11:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.97,0:11:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Ouch...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.89,0:11:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me! That hurts!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.11,0:11:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She's got a cute ass.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.29,0:11:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.91,0:11:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.44,0:11:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You little punk.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.67,0:11:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.71,0:11:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Motherfucker!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.67,0:11:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit, it's the cops!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.45,0:11:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.16,0:11:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll regret it!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.15,0:12:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.26,0:12:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, are {\i1}you{\i0} okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.11,0:12:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hang on!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.82,0:12:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Superman!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.74,0:12:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh shit! Why am I in someone's room?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.73,0:12:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No... Pervert...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.24,0:12:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta go!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.38,0:12:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, though...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.19,0:12:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This certainly is my own room. \NWhy, then...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.43,0:12:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.92,0:12:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.19,0:13:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a real pain dragging you home \Nwhen you were dead drunk.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.92,0:13:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you did that?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.02,0:13:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You really don't remember?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.48,0:13:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.63,0:13:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even what you did to me? {lit: the thing about me (referring to junpei saving her)}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.85,0:13:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,"What I did to you"?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.01,0:13:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me I've done\N the unthinkable to you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.02,0:13:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh shit...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.81,0:13:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.95,0:13:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my first time. {[being saved]...?}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.40,0:14:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If I get pregnant, what will you do? {idk anymore}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.16,0:14:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I was drunk,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.16,0:14:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,so I don't remember.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.83,0:14:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.25,0:14:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.15,0:14:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, are you close to Mina Yoshiko?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.70,0:14:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.18,0:14:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you even have her number.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.97,0:14:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really. We just talked once at work.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.42,0:14:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know she was married to the {\i1}grand fromage{\i0} film director, Shibuya Shozo?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.88,0:14:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Shibuya Shozo?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.05,0:14:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They even had a child, I think.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.99,0:14:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? So she's a single divorcee, then?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.62,0:14:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But right now, she's the mistress \Nof Nanto Conglomerate's president. {/conglomerate}{unsure if this "nanto" is not just "some"; it was "nanbu / 南部" in manga}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.27,0:14:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so that's how it is?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.34,0:15:01.13,Thought,,0,0,0,,Nanto Daigo and Mina Yoshiko, huh? {南to 大吾}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.00,0:15:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wanna have lunch?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.89,0:15:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you're an aspiring film director?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.43,0:15:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess so.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.66,0:15:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not easy.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.03,0:15:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're charging straight\N at your goal. That's impressive!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.58,0:15:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, what's your name?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.72,0:15:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoko. Mikami Shoko.\NNice to meet you, Koganei-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.19,0:15:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? How'd you know my name?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.70,0:15:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw your business card.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.20,0:15:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yikes! I need to be somewhere!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.41,0:15:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, hey...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.57,0:15:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, bye!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.45,0:15:36.86,Thought,,0,0,0,,Shoko-san, huh? \NShe's like a good fairy.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.86,0:15:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Junpei-kun?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.68,0:15:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Miwa-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.97,0:15:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Since when are you friends \Nwith the idol singer Mikami Shoko?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.30,0:15:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Idol singer? Her?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.57,0:15:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, even if she's \Na bit past her prime. {on the wane (e.g. popularity of something); decline of one's fortunes}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.18,0:15:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So you rescued Mikami Shoko?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.92,0:15:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I woke up at my apartment. {lit: and then [she took me] to my flat - intentional to create misunderstanding}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.96,0:15:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's where she spent the night, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.55,0:16:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But nothing happened between us!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.88,0:16:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure what I'm supposed to think.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.78,0:16:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, p-please believe me!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.70,0:16:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I only have you on my mind!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.07,0:16:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I'll believe you.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.00,0:16:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.53,0:16:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You want me to star?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.64,0:16:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Co-starring with Takamura Toru and me. \NMy manager will contact you for details. {says nakamura for some reason but it actually must be takamura}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.03,0:16:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I look forward to it.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.51,0:16:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Junpei! Mina Yoshiko called.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.07,0:16:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She wanted you to meet some producer.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.12,0:16:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Junpei, cut out the solo act. {lit: individual play}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.35,0:16:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're defecting to Mina Yoshiko? {lit: sales promotion; hard selling - not sure what he means}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.02,0:16:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd never do that!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.82,0:16:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just a stepping-stone to you?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.58,0:16:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now {\i1}that's{\i0} going too far!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.24,0:16:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Junpei.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.57,0:16:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd understand if you quit Apollo Productions.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.41,0:16:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Not you too, Chief!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.11,0:16:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.73,0:17:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What you did was a major slap \Nin the face of Apollo Productions. {breach of faith; breach of trust; act of disloyalty}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.90,0:17:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm going\N to turn down Mina's offer!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.28,0:17:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd let such a great chance slip?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.47,0:17:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I think an offer like that \Ncomes once in a lifetime.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.55,0:17:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all grumbling now, \Nbut they'll see you off with a smile.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.61,0:17:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.08,0:17:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never leave Apollo Productions!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.26,0:17:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't have any reservations because of me.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.90,0:17:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,In this trade, everyone hopes to make it big\N one day and move on to the major leagues.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.25,0:17:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That thought never even crossed my mind.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.93,0:17:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You should go after your dreams\Nwithout hesitation, Junpei-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.17,0:17:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But I love you, Miwa-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.65,0:17:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And I want to keep working\N with you forever!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.58,0:17:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're saying?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.31,0:17:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Miwa-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.61,0:17:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm serious.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.92,0:18:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But you never let me see your true self, \Nonly the mask that you choose to wear! {very unsure}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.21,0:18:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.44,0:18:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Then show how you truly feel! {/your true face}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.97,0:18:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Junpei-kun...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.05,0:18:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go meet Mina Yoshiko.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.47,0:18:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go! You'll regret it!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.62,0:18:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.89,0:18:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're turning it down?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.94,0:18:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.76,0:18:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But Ujiki-chan said \NI can have you all to myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.12,0:18:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He did?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.92,0:18:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and for this next film, I'm planning to hire everyone from Apollo Productions as staff.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.62,0:18:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.92,0:18:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,In return, I'll finance the next Apollo Productions flick.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.18,0:18:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ujiki-chan and I go back a long way. {since we met at the studio}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.79,0:18:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He may be making TV shows now, but he used to be an outstanding assistant director.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.95,0:18:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very grateful for the opportunity.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.86,0:18:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't thank me yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.45,0:19:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I still don't know what terms\N my boss will lay down to finance it.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.72,0:19:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We're talking about Nanto Daigo, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.10,0:19:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. So you already know?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.28,0:19:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This whole Apollo affair hinges on \Ngetting Nanto Daigo's permission.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.00,0:19:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.62,0:19:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.39,0:19:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.94,0:19:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You really think you can pull in\N young viewers with that?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.58,0:19:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Veteran or not, Director Shibuya is just not about that.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.83,0:19:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying he's too old-fashioned?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.64,0:19:27.94,Top,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.94,0:19:30.34,Top,,0,0,0,,Your times have passed. {kimira - maybe referring both to their marriage and their popularity?}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.33,0:19:35.15,Top,,0,0,0,,Our audience is eager to move on.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.65,0:19:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't have to be that way!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.60,0:19:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,To boost appeal for younger audiences, \Nwe'll cast idol singer Mikami Shoko in the lead.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.37,0:19:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll also staff it with young people \Nwho are passionate about filmmaking.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.47,0:19:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You still don't get it?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.34,0:19:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You no longer have the sex appeal \Nto attract young male viewers.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.51,0:19:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how you can be \Nsure of that so easily.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.73,0:20:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying that you, Mina Yoshiko, can still make a young man get hard?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.18,0:20:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.68,0:20:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Then prove it to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.86,0:20:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If you manage to convince me, I'll fund it.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.51,0:20:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.82,0:20:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll see this young man right here \Nget hard because of me.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.41,0:20:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.06,0:20:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. Can't wait to see you try.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.51,0:20:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep your eyes on me.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.76,0:20:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.85,0:21:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.76,0:21:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not aroused in the slightest!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.62,0:21:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just warming up. \NDon't rush me!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.44,0:21:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.73,0:21:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Well?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.89,0:21:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How's this?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.13,0:21:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Junpei-kun, what's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.75,0:21:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm truly touched by you undressing for me, \Nbut I'm not really feeling it down there.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.77,0:21:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand. It only appealed to the noble part of your soul. {lit: you felt it with lofty; sublime; noble heart}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.36,0:21:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That means you can perceive me \Nas more than just a sexual object.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.41,0:21:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to stop fooling yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.53,0:21:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You simply no longer have any appeal.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.74,0:21:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong, Nanto-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.30,0:21:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina is very sexy and alluring!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.18,0:21:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She's plenty appealing!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.73,0:21:56.68,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Really? Why can't you get hard, then?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.47,0:21:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because... something's missing.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:00.41,0:22:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I think something is missing.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.47,0:22:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Something...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:08.33,0:22:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:10.33,0:22:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There! Now everyone in the opposite building can see Mina Yoshiko nude!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:13.92,0:22:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to embarrass me? \NYou won't get away with it!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:16.92,0:22:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Give them all a good long look of your body.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:20.90,0:22:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Stop that!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:22.50,0:22:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it, please watch.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:24.00,0:22:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:25.06,0:22:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! Go!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:25.98,0:22:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! Are you out of your mind?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:27.92,0:22:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No! What are you doing? Stop it!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:30.60,0:22:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Windowsill sex is an instant arouser! {lit: sex by the window is great fun}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:36.50,0:22:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:39.29,0:22:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:46.07,0:22:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,His erection is strong enough\N to support Yoshiko's entire body! {lit: symbol or erection - idk what he means, maybe that his arousement materialized into that mushroom/wood we're seeing?}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:49.26,0:22:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What amazing power!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:52.03,0:22:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough! You've convinced me!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:57.09,0:23:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This natural, off-the-screen form of yours is still mesmerizing. {lit: when not acting}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:00.80,0:23:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Your rod also has tremendous power.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:05.17,0:23:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I lose. I'll give you 1.5 billion to make this movie.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:08.97,0:23:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:09.90,0:23:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:10.52,0:23:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Junpei-kun, thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:12.51,0:23:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I also ought to thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:15.03,0:23:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been impotent for five years, but seeing Yoshiko just now, it sprang back to life! See?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:19.05,0:23:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Look!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:21.91,0:23:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! What a hard-on! {/pounding/pulsating}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:24.15,0:23:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my! That's wonderful, darling!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:26.55,0:23:28.18,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Yoshiko!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:29.76,0:23:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:33.01,0:23:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave you kids alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:35.39,0:23:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's nice!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:37.26,0:23:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, darling!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:39.84,0:23:43.15,Thought,,0,0,0,,Our fortunes are changing. \NNow things are getting interesting! {something appearing from a place one wouldn't expect; something said as a joke actually happening; a horse from a gourd​}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:44.30,0:23:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:45.73,0:23:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Moron. Moron. Moron!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:49.94,0:23:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:52.95,0:23:55.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This new big-budget movie, \N{\i1}Who Saw the Tears?{\i0}, {their posters throughout the episode say "mita" (who saw?) but in spoken text they always say "miseta" (who showed?); I'll stick to the latter, though I'm not really sure and I don't think it matters anyway}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:55.66,0:24:00.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,will star Mikami Shoko and co-star\N Mina Yoshiko and Takamura Toru.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:00.25,0:24:03.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With the renowned Shibuya Shozo in the director's seat,
Dialogue: 10,0:24:03.62,0:24:08.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and the full cooperation of Apollo Productions, \Nfilming will begin in the summer. {crank in}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:08.40,0:24:11.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Miwa-san was asked to help \NDirector Shibuya with the storyboards,
Dialogue: 10,0:24:11.83,0:24:14.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and I was selected as the third assistant.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:14.51,0:24:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And here's to our future hit! Cheers!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:19.42,0:24:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:21.39,0:24:25.18,Top,,0,0,0,,Who would've thought Shibuya Shozo would cast a fading idol in his film?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:25.18,0:24:28.52,Top,,0,0,0,,And also complement it with a hag and a newbie. It's sad, right? {lit: and her costars are obatarian and clear - obatarian is "rude, selfish middle-aged woman​ - Colloquial, blend of おばさん and バタリアン ("The Return of the Living Dead")" but I have no idea what to make of the "clear", can't find this line in manga either; maybe "clear" as in "clean slate" as in "someone with no prior experience"?}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:28.85,0:24:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare they say that!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:30.40,0:24:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Just let it slide.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:37.87,0:24:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We're totally out of place here, aren't we?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:40.27,0:24:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:41.93,0:24:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Koganei-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:44.50,0:24:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Shibuya Shozo's chief of staff, Gondo.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:47.52,0:24:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Nakajima, the first assistant.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:49.16,0:24:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my first time doing actual cinema,\N so please take care of me. {actually "live-action" but the porn they filmed previously was clearly also live-action and not animation, so he means "films for the theaters" as opposed to porn}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:52.17,0:24:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It was rash of Shibuya to appoint\N a complete rookie as his third assistant.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:55.78,0:24:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It took me eight years to get there.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:58.06,0:24:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:58.68,0:25:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The path of an assistant director is thorny.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:01.78,0:25:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little advice as your superior:\N real films and porn have nothing in common!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:06.74,0:25:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But I never... {sonna}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:07.10,0:25:08.90,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Well, I hope we get along.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:13.97,0:25:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Junpei-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:18.11,0:25:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? You still haven't said a word.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:20.06,0:25:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I work in that environment?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:22.36,0:25:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even know the basics of filmmaking.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:24.30,0:25:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have come!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:33.57,0:25:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:34.64,0:25:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're perfectly capable.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:36.48,0:25:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If you sprint right out of the gate, \Nyou'll be gasping for air in no time.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:39.54,0:25:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give them a taste of your talent. {lit: part/glimpse is enough - meaning "no need to show them all your cards at once"}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:41.18,0:25:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Miwa-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:25:42.32,0:25:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's show those jerks just what we AV people are made of!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:45.18,0:25:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Be strong. You're a man, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:46.95,0:25:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:56.17,0:26:00.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And so, the filming began for "Who Saw the Tears?" {crank-in}
Dialogue: 10,0:26:01.85,0:26:05.64,NarTop,,0,0,0,,The story is about a female teacher and her daughter, Hitomi.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:05.64,0:26:08.04,NarTop,,0,0,0,,It's a tale of love and hatred.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:08.04,0:26:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's do a serious take now.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:09.96,0:26:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready? Action!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:11.83,0:26:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, cutie. Wanna play with us?
Dialogue: 10,0:26:16.45,0:26:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,How 'bout you take off your panties?
Dialogue: 10,0:26:18.93,0:26:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have known you were like this.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:21.28,0:26:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no! That's not how you take them off!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:23.47,0:26:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no feeling in it!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:25.80,0:26:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No girl's shyness!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:27.31,0:26:28.92,Overlap,,0,0,0,,But isn't Hitomi acting tough,
Dialogue: 10,0:26:28.92,0:26:30.48,Overlap,,0,0,0,,pretending she's ready to undress?
Dialogue: 10,0:26:30.83,0:26:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but she's only pretending to be okay with it.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:33.24,0:26:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. One more take!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:35.05,0:26:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Action!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:36.73,0:26:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut! No, that's no good!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:38.31,0:26:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:39.40,0:26:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not that! Cut! Cut!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:42.48,0:26:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a coffee break, everyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:44.20,0:26:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna go to my room?
Dialogue: 10,0:26:46.00,0:26:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:26:47.00,0:26:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. You need a break.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:50.77,0:26:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. Just relax.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:53.69,0:26:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, think of this as the actual filming.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:01.27,0:27:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:02.31,0:27:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:07.85,0:27:09.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Miwa's plan worked.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:09.70,0:27:13.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The awkwardness of her first time\N with another woman helped Shoko-chan
Dialogue: 10,0:27:13.13,0:27:14.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,put on a convincing act.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:14.78,0:27:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're adorable, Shoko-chan. \NYou know that?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:22.19,0:27:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to remember this feeling.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:24.75,0:27:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready. Action!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:31.03,0:27:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Fucking brat!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:34.11,0:27:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think you are?!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:35.96,0:27:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you calling a brat?!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:38.73,0:27:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut, cut, cut, cut!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:42.65,0:27:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops, did I accidentally flash it? {lit: I wonder if you saw my naked cunny}
Dialogue: 10,0:27:45.89,0:27:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That was great, just great! Okay! Good!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:49.02,0:27:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It was so much better when you put your feelings into it!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:52.92,0:27:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure are a sweet little thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:55.20,0:27:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That was really great! Okay! Good!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:57.56,0:28:02.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Next day, we started shooting the scene of the students assaulting Hitomi's mother at school. {/violate/outrage}
Dialogue: 10,0:28:02.03,0:28:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready... Action!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:04.85,0:28:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:07.10,0:28:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:28:12.90,0:28:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:14.63,0:28:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, time to get into action! {idk}
Dialogue: 10,0:28:19.51,0:28:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So how was it? \NYou liked it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:21.99,0:28:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's stop this.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:22.98,0:28:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I do something?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:24.04,0:28:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You really don't get it?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:25.48,0:28:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just too small. \NI can't act convincingly scared of that. {lit: I don't feel like acting}
Dialogue: 10,0:28:28.96,0:28:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Did you mean my...\NHuh, my willy? Shit!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:32.95,0:28:35.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Mina Yoshiko-san nominated me,\N Koganei Junpei,
Dialogue: 10,0:28:35.88,0:28:39.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,to replace Toru Takamura as the lead, \Nso it's gonna get real now!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:55.65,0:28:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:04.09,0:29:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Not there! {idk, maybe "nice"}
