Dialogue: 10,0:29:17.21,0:29:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oops...
Dialogue: 10,0:29:32.57,0:29:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How's Director Shibuya?
Dialogue: 10,0:29:35.49,0:29:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He had a stroke. {cerebral thrombosis}
Dialogue: 10,0:29:37.00,0:29:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll need to rest for a while.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:41.51,0:29:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You must find a deputy director to finish the film.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:48.37,0:29:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoko. Do your best until the end.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:52.67,0:29:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:56.87,0:29:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Miwa-kun...
Dialogue: 10,0:29:58.80,0:29:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:30:00.29,0:30:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you be so kind\N and replace me as the director?
Dialogue: 10,0:30:06.25,0:30:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 10,0:30:08.37,0:30:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:10.07,0:30:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you helped me\N with the storyboards,
Dialogue: 10,0:30:12.66,0:30:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you understand my vision better than anyone else.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:16.56,0:30:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, take care of it.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:19.49,0:30:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:30:23.14,0:30:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A director, whether of an adult video \Nor a major motion picture,
Dialogue: 10,0:30:29.41,0:30:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,must be able to manage the staff,
Dialogue: 10,0:30:31.05,0:30:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,give accurate acting instructions to the cast,
Dialogue: 10,0:30:34.56,0:30:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and have passion for creating the film.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:38.03,0:30:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Loving the work you do \Nis what matters the most!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:42.74,0:30:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You have that in you, Miwa-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:45.07,0:30:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Miwa-san, please do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:46.58,0:30:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree. Please help us!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:48.92,0:30:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Miwa-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:54.65,0:30:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Director Shibuya, I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:57.99,0:30:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:59.43,0:31:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We're right behind you. \NDon't give up, Miwa.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:01.92,0:31:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:03.09,0:31:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:03.90,0:31:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Show them what an AV director is made of. {lit: pride/guts of video}
Dialogue: 10,0:31:08.80,0:31:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:10.65,0:31:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He bypassed me, his chief assistant, \Nand appointed some amateur porn director!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:16.18,0:31:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Gondo-san, she still can't film anything without our help.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:21.46,0:31:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:23.50,0:31:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just see her try!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:25.72,0:31:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Porn director? Don't make me laugh! {lit: what can a ero video director do}
Dialogue: 10,0:31:28.17,0:31:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad news, people!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:30.35,0:31:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A boycott?
Dialogue: 10,0:31:31.40,0:31:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Both the cameraman and\N the chief assistant protested. {"to instigate; to stir up; to incite; to agitate" but idk what she means}
Dialogue: 10,0:31:34.12,0:31:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How did it come to this?
Dialogue: 10,0:31:36.45,0:31:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go beg them not to quit the project! {/to assist us}
Dialogue: 10,0:31:44.75,0:31:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, gentlemen, help us finish the movie!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:47.90,0:31:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We need you.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:49.19,0:31:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No fucking way!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:51.02,0:31:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Gondo-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:53.23,0:31:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did they send {\i1}you{\i0}?
Dialogue: 10,0:31:55.24,0:31:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't "director" Wakaba Miwa face me personally? Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:31:58.14,0:31:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just protocol. {https://jisho.org/word/%E7%AD%8B}
Dialogue: 10,0:32:00.35,0:32:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,At a film studio, if you don't follow protocol, \Neveryone will turn their back on you! {/be uncooperative}
Dialogue: 10,0:32:05.34,0:32:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better fucking remember that, \Nyou greenhorn!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:13.77,0:32:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help us.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:16.55,0:32:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Gondo-san, we need your cooperation.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:21.13,0:32:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:26.57,0:32:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You jerks! You're still not satisfied?! {idk}
Dialogue: 10,0:32:29.42,0:32:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 10,0:32:30.00,0:32:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just gutless and talentless cowards! {small-minded; petty; cowardly; chicken-hearted}
Dialogue: 10,0:32:32.80,0:32:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Junpei-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:33.94,0:32:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That little shit...
Dialogue: 10,0:32:39.69,0:32:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you've done it.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:41.05,0:32:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Junpei-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:46.15,0:32:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Asshole!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:48.87,0:32:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:57.75,0:32:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sto...
Dialogue: 10,0:32:59.70,0:33:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:14.26,0:33:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Junpei, enough!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:19.18,0:33:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Miwa, if they won't cooperate, forget them. We'll shoot that movie ourselves.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:23.06,0:33:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be your chief assistant. \NDirector, we can do it.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:27.53,0:33:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This scene is the film's climax.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:30.83,0:33:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The college students \Nare about to violate Hitomi.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:34.13,0:33:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when her mother, Mina-san, the teacher, rushes in to save her.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:39.09,0:33:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,She's just a porn director,
Dialogue: 10,0:33:41.45,0:33:43.25,Top,,0,0,0,,yet she acts like a big shot.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:43.69,0:33:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Damn it all... She just stole the spotlight from me, Takamura Toru! {lit: I'm not the only center of attention}
Dialogue: 10,0:33:47.94,0:33:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,J-Just you watch, wench! \NWe'll make a total mess of this movie!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:52.22,0:33:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys, I'll let'cha guys in \Non a little secret.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:55.54,0:33:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Get closer.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:58.45,0:34:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Bang Shoko?!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:00.05,0:34:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Shh! Don't let everyone hear you.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:03.17,0:34:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,During the actual take, \NI'll get my thing into Shoko for real!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:07.53,0:34:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's shoot!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:09.10,0:34:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:10.84,0:34:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Action!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:15.43,0:34:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:19.89,0:34:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:34:27.73,0:34:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Stop...
Dialogue: 10,0:34:30.47,0:34:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too loud.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:34.80,0:34:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,My pan{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 10,0:34:37.55,0:34:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:34:39.63,0:34:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You boys. What are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:34:42.34,0:34:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Shaddup! I'm gonna fuck her! {unsure, maybe "get lost"}
Dialogue: 10,0:34:52.07,0:34:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop this now!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:53.02,0:34:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck off!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:56.73,0:34:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:34:58.28,0:34:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:58.97,0:34:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop struggling!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:03.27,0:35:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:05.54,0:35:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 10,0:35:09.59,0:35:11.71,Thought,,0,0,0,,Th-That feels nice...
Dialogue: 10,0:35:21.15,0:35:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Fucking hell! {gerogero = ribbit but also "that's gross!; disgusting!​"}
Dialogue: 10,0:35:22.02,0:35:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What the fuck?
Dialogue: 10,0:35:23.70,0:35:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,D'you like it? {/like this?}
Dialogue: 10,0:35:25.10,0:35:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You fucking grandma!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:26.54,0:35:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go! Let go of it!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:38.61,0:35:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Drop it, you!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:40.10,0:35:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:41.51,0:35:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How's this? {dou}
Dialogue: 10,0:35:45.18,0:35:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, go, go!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:48.45,0:35:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the terrifying Ashura for you! {恐怖の阿修羅だ - literally "ashura of horror" - referring to ashura having hands and faces on all sides, just like she does when spinning}
Dialogue: 10,0:36:14.99,0:36:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 10,0:36:17.74,0:36:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You like it?
Dialogue: 10,0:36:30.19,0:36:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,To save my beloved daughter, \NI'd even become a vampire if I had to.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:34.46,0:36:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 10,0:36:36.12,0:36:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitomi.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:37.38,0:36:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:38.50,0:36:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitomi!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:45.01,0:36:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:47.47,0:36:52.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Thanks to the tireless efforts of Miwa-san and the Apollo Productions staff,
Dialogue: 10,0:36:52.04,0:36:53.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,we finished filming. {crank up}
Dialogue: 10,0:36:53.75,0:36:57.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Released during the New Year season, the movie was a big hit,
Dialogue: 10,0:36:57.38,0:37:00.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,largely because Miwa-san substituted\N as director for Shibuya.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:00.30,0:37:05.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It also shot Shoko-chan back to stardom, \Nand everything turned out fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:09.54,0:37:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:10.56,0:37:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And with that, our Apollo Productions now deals in major motion pictures too. {/large video}{unsure, maybe he means "is going to film a major flick of its own"}
Dialogue: 10,0:37:15.17,0:37:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to the financial support of Mina Yoshiko-san here.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:18.00,0:37:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, everyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:19.60,0:37:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The movie topped the list \Nof New Year releases.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:23.24,0:37:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to that, Mikami Shoko's \Npopularity has risen dramatically.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:26.54,0:37:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to think that with that, \Nwe made things right with my Shoko. {/made amends/repaid - fuck knows what for}
Dialogue: 10,0:37:30.59,0:37:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is, Shoko is my real daughter \Nwith Director Shibuya.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:34.45,0:37:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We divorced when she was in grade school,\N so we sent her to a fine arts boarding school. {no clue what's this poriporo, I'm only getting polypropylene-related results, and it's not in manga; it sounds fancy so I'll wager a guess it's a name of some "school for idols"}
Dialogue: 10,0:37:39.81,0:37:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how it is?
Dialogue: 10,0:37:41.54,0:37:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Good thing nothing happened between you two, Junpei-kun. {referring to when she dragged him home}
Dialogue: 10,0:37:45.25,0:37:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I will also take this opportunity to retire from acting and become a producer.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:50.39,0:37:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I look forward to working with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:51.80,0:37:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,She's retiring?
Dialogue: 10,0:37:52.56,0:37:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What a waste!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:54.57,0:37:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that makes Mikami Shoko\N the shadow savior of Apollo Productions?
Dialogue: 10,0:37:58.33,0:37:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems so.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:59.76,0:38:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Junpei-kun is my prince. {sounds like the roles in a fairy tale or soemthing}
Dialogue: 10,0:38:01.84,0:38:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:21.21,0:38:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels so chilly and refreshing!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:23.13,0:38:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You've let your true feelings show. {lit: today's miwa-san has a true face}
Dialogue: 10,0:38:25.67,0:38:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's race, Miwa-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:29.73,0:38:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, I'll always be by your side!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:33.22,0:38:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that? What side? {unsure if she just didn't hear well}
Dialogue: 10,0:38:36.43,0:38:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I can be so cheesy sometimes! {lit: well said, I can do it too}
Dialogue: 10,0:38:43.33,0:38:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh geez! Where are you hiding now? Come on!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:49.23,0:38:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, my second adventure was also a crazy circus!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:55.83,0:38:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And with that, everyone...
Dialogue: 10,0:38:58.00,0:39:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,have a nice day! {gokigen? no clue}
Dialogue: 10,0:42:09.95,0:42:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello! Junpei here!
Dialogue: 10,0:42:11.91,0:42:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you like my first movie?
Dialogue: 10,0:42:15.15,0:42:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then! In the next episode of \N{\i1}A Good Time for an Adventure{\i0}...
Dialogue: 10,0:42:18.18,0:42:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Returning to the AV world again, \NMiwa and I scouted out a certain girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:23.31,0:42:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But actually, it turns out\N she's Director Shibuya's secretary!
Dialogue: 10,0:42:28.44,0:42:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell, Junpei?
Dialogue: 10,0:42:31.15,0:42:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna cast my secretary in a porno?
Dialogue: 10,0:42:35.61,0:42:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't allow it!
Dialogue: 10,0:42:36.76,0:42:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never allow it.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:38.66,0:42:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does it have to be you?! \NYou goddamn weasel! {lit: what a delightful thing to say - no idea what he means}
Dialogue: 10,0:42:43.12,0:42:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you get all the action?! \NFine. I'll remember this.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:48.21,0:42:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That said, Director Shibuya seems really delighted and moved by that. {no clue}
Dialogue: 10,0:42:51.80,0:42:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's the craziest part!
Dialogue: 10,0:42:53.30,0:42:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, that secretary
Dialogue: 10,0:42:55.20,0:42:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,was kidnapped and held captive just before we were supposed to start filming.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:11.68,0:43:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,When Junpei learns about this, \Nhe rushes to save her,
Dialogue: 10,0:43:15.39,0:43:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,but instead he gets beaten to a pulp\N and has to retreat. {lit: on his way back - that doesn't make sense to retreat before he saved her right?}
Dialogue: 10,0:43:18.24,0:43:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, Junpei-kun, how sloppy can you be?
Dialogue: 10,0:43:21.58,0:43:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I can't help it, Miwa-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:24.16,0:43:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just that weak.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:39.71,0:43:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Junpei-kun, don't lose heart.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:41.84,0:43:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We have an Unopened Locker of our own. {あかずのロッカー - apparently, there was a horror show that ran in the 90s that had an episode titled that about a guy who entered a locker but couldn't open it and was scrapped inside it, but it's probably unrelated; akazu generally means "unopened/unopening/impossible to open" so maybe they mean "the locker we never opened"; akazu no ma also means "room that is forbidden to enter; locked room; unopened room" but I'm still not sure if it's related}
Dialogue: 10,0:43:44.85,0:43:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A forbidden locker?
Dialogue: 10,0:43:51.50,0:43:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time on {\i1}A Good Time for an Adventure{\i0}, \Nepisode three,
Dialogue: 10,0:43:54.48,0:43:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,"Apollo Guerrilla Film Crew Arrives!" {アポロ軍団ゲリラ撮影隊参上!}
Dialogue: 10,0:43:57.78,0:44:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Dangerous guerrilla filming and a series of mishaps!
Dialogue: 10,0:44:03.44,0:44:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally, it's also full of sex \Nand 120% more fun!
Dialogue: 10,0:44:09.28,0:44:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't miss it, guys!
Dialogue: 10,0:44:11.97,0:44:13.39,Top,,0,0,0,,Don't miss it, guys!
