Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.04,0:00:42.64,English,,0,0,0,,I chased you to the motor pool, "Let me walk you home"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.64,0:00:48.33,English,,0,0,0,,Putting my ulterior motives on the side seat
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.33,0:00:54.41,English,,0,0,0,,Whoa, but the radio is giving me bad news
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.41,0:00:57.62,English,,0,0,0,,My mood is sold out, you're only joking
