Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.36,0:39:21.70,English,,0,0,0,,Asphalt, the lonely building {same booklet; アスファルト 孤独のビルディング\N立ちすくむ 見慣れた都会\N時の流れに背中を押され\N生きるのも悪くはないさだけど\N\N作り笑いの パズリング・デイズ\N過ごしたくないだけなのさ\N\Nターミナル 仮面の群れを\N眺め疲れて コンコース歩いてみる\Nあと少しで P.M.5: 00 o'clock \Nworking time 脱け出せるけど\N\N出口は無いさ バズリング・テイズ\N独り 明日へ向かう \N\NJust a puzzle 合わす様に\Nリスキーなまま生きてくしかない \N“現実”に Never say no/\N\N作り笑いの バズリング・デイズ\N過したくないからさ \N\NIt's a puzzle 合わす様に\Nリスキーなまま生きてくしかない \N“現実”に Never say no/}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.91,0:39:28.80,English,,0,0,0,,Standing frozen in the familiar city
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.80,0:39:34.98,English,,0,0,0,,Pushed by the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.31,0:39:43.00,English,,0,0,0,,It's not so bad to be alive
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.00,0:39:55.20,English,,0,0,0,,But I just don't want to spend\N these puzzling days faking a smile
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.66,0:40:02.37,English,,0,0,0,,Tired of looking at the crowd of masks
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.44,0:40:11.43,English,,0,0,0,,At the terminal, I walk down the concourse
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.26,0:40:15.47,English,,0,0,0,,It's almost
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.67,0:40:19.58,English,,0,0,0,,5 o'clock PM
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.18,0:40:24.97,English,,0,0,0,,I can escape from my working time
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.73,0:40:29.63,English,,0,0,0,,But there's no way out of the puzzling days
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.63,0:40:36.39,English,,0,0,0,,I'm alone, heading toward tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.24,0:40:43.14,English,,0,0,0,,Just a puzzle that I have to piece together
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.14,0:40:50.48,English,,0,0,0,,I have no choice but to live riskily
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.48,0:40:57.89,English,,0,0,0,,Never say no to reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.12,0:41:36.86,English,,0,0,0,,I just don't want to spend\N these puzzling days faking a smile
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.77,0:41:43.64,English,,0,0,0,,It's a puzzle that I have to piece together
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.64,0:41:50.98,English,,0,0,0,,I have no choice but to live riskily
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.98,0:41:55.00,English,,0,0,0,,Never say no to...
